<h4>Kolodion</h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
    You have to defeat Kolodion using only Magic. Fortunately, recoil and poison both work, so this isn't very difficult. He does have 5 forms which are fought sequentially (man, ogre, troll, dark beast and black demon), so bring enough supplies and use the Protect from Magic prayer if necessary. 
